---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight">The Problem &amp; Our Fix</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        WordPress.org has dozens of plugins that do the same thing - most locking the useful bits behind a paywall. We pick the problem, build one plugin that solves it properly, and give it away. Here's how.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="text-center group">
        <div class="mx-auto size-16 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/40 group-hover:bg-blue-200 dark:group-hover:bg-blue-900/60 transition-colors duration-200">
          <Icon name="lucide:terminal" class="size-8 text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">One Problem, One Plugin</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          We identify a real need - admin tools, WooCommerce add-ons, performance tweaks - and build one focused plugin that handles it well. No feature bloat, no "upgrade for more."
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center group">
        <div class="mx-auto size-16 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/40 group-hover:bg-blue-200 dark:group-hover:bg-blue-900/60 transition-colors duration-200">
          <Icon name="lucide:users" class="size-8 text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Built by the Community</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          Anyone can contribute - code, bug reports, ideas. PRs get real reviews, we catch bugs together, and the plugins get better because more eyes are on them.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center group">
        <div class="mx-auto size-16 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/40 group-hover:bg-blue-200 dark:group-hover:bg-blue-900/60 transition-colors duration-200">
          <Icon name="lucide:infinity" class="size-8 text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Free Forever</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          No "pro" tier coming next quarter. These plugins stay free and open source. We keep going through donations and community contributions, not paywalls.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
